        </div>
        <!-- Therapeutic Recommendations -->
        <div class="section recommendations">
            <h3>Personalized Therapeutic Recommendations</h3>
            <div class="rec-category">
                <div class="rec-title">🧘 Immediate Cannabimimetic Interventions (0-2 weeks)</div>
                <ul class="rec-list">
                    <li>Begin daily 15-minute meditation practice to naturally boost AEA production</li>
                    <li>Implement cold exposure therapy (2-3 minutes daily) to enhance eCBome signaling</li>
                    <li>Start breathwork sessions (4-7-8 breathing) to reduce cortisol and support CB1 function</li>
                    <li>Eliminate inflammatory foods (processed sugars, trans fats) for 2 weeks</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rec-category">
                <div class="rec-title">🌿 Phytocannabinoid Therapy (2-8 weeks)</div>
                <ul class="rec-list">
                    <li>Consider CBD therapy: Start with 10mg daily, increase to 25mg based on response</li>
                    <li>Evening cannabis use (indica-dominant) may support natural AEA peak and sexual health</li>
                    <li>CBG supplementation (5-10mg) for CB2 receptor support and inflammation reduction</li>
                    <li>Terpene therapy: Linalool and myrcene for stress reduction and sleep optimization</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rec-category">
                <div class="rec-title">💊 Nutritional & Supplement Support</div>
                <ul class="rec-list">
                    <li>Omega-3 fatty acids: 2000mg EPA/DHA daily to support endocannabinoid synthesis</li>
                    <li>Magnesium glycinate: 400mg before bed for GABA-eCBome interaction</li>
                    <li>Adaptogenic herbs: Ashwagandha (300mg) to reduce cortisol and support hormonal balance</li>
                    <li>Probiotic supplementation: Focus on Lactobacillus strains for gut-eCBome axis</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rec-category">
                <div class="rec-title">💑 Sexual Health Optimization</div>
                <ul class="rec-list">
                    <li>Coordinate intimacy with evening AEA peak (7-9 PM) for enhanced experience</li>
                    <li>Consider bioidentical hormone consultation for estradiol optimization</li>
                    <li>Stress reduction specifically before intimate moments to optimize eCBome function</li>
                    <li>Partner meditation or breathwork to synchronize eCBome states</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rec-category">
                <div class="rec-title">🧬 Personalized Medicine Considerations</div>
                <ul class="rec-list">
                    <li>Genetic testing recommended: COMT, FAAH, CNR1 polymorphisms for personalized dosing</li>
                    <li>Microbiome analysis to optimize gut-eCBome axis interventions</li>
                    <li>Regular eCBome biomarker monitoring every 3 months</li>
                    <li>Consider psychedelic-assisted therapy consultation for trauma-informed eCBome healing</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Drug Interactions & Safety -->
        <div class="section">
            <h3>Pharmaceutical Interactions & Safety</h3>
            <div class="disclaimer">
                <h4>⚠️ Important Safety Information</h4>
                <p>Current medications may interact with cannabinoid therapy. Monitor closely for enhanced sedative effects with benzodiazepines, potential changes in antidepressant effectiveness, and altered pain medication requirements. Always consult with your healthcare provider before making changes to medication regimens.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>eCBome Intelligent Integrative Health Record</strong></p>
            <p>This report represents a comprehensive analysis of your endocannabinoidome system and should be used in conjunction with professional medical advice.</p>
            <p>Generated on ${new Date().toLocaleString()}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        // Receptor Status Chart
        const receptorCtx = document.getElementById('receptorChart').getContext('2d');
        new Chart(receptorCtx, {
            type: 'radar',
            data: {
                labels: ${JSON.stringify(reportData.analysisResults.receptorStatus.map(r => r.name))},
                datasets: [{
                    label: 'Current Function',
                    data: ${JSON.stringify(reportData.analysisResults.receptorStatus.map(r => r.score))},
                    backgroundColor: 'rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2)',
