              </div>
              <div className="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
                <h4 className="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Afternoon (12-6 PM)</h4>
                <ul className="text-sm text-blue-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>• AEA rising, cortisol falling</li>
                  <li>• Peak 2-AG levels</li>
                  <li>• Optimal for social activities</li>
                  <li>• Light exercise beneficial</li>
